<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" appName="Prep & Provide" lastUpdated="July 2026">

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>Legacy Renovations SGF</strong> ("we," "us," or "our")
    collects, uses, and protects information in connection with the <strong>Prep &amp; Provide</strong>
    application ("the App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and being straightforward
    about how your data is handled.
  </p>

  <p>
    Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:dustin@legacyrenovationssgf.com" style="color: var(--heritage-gold);">dustin@legacyrenovationssgf.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect only what is necessary to provide the App's features:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Your email address and a securely hashed password, used to authenticate you and maintain your account.</li>
    <li><strong>Meal plans:</strong> Weekly and custom meal plans you create within the App.</li>
    <li><strong>Recipes:</strong> Recipes you save, create, or import into the App.</li>
    <li><strong>Grocery lists:</strong> Shopping lists generated from your meal plans or added manually.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect your name, location, phone number, device identifiers, advertising identifiers, usage analytics, or any other personal data beyond what is listed above.</p>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your information is used solely to provide and support the App's functionality:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>To authenticate your identity when you log in.</li>
    <li>To store and sync your meal plans, recipes, and grocery lists across sessions and devices.</li>
    <li>To enable Alexa voice integration so you can access your recipes and grocery list hands-free.</li>
    <li>To respond to support requests you initiate with us.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not use your information for advertising, marketing profiling, or any automated decision-making.</p>

  <h2>3. Alexa Integration</h2>
  <p>
    Prep &amp; Provide supports Amazon Alexa voice integration via <strong>OAuth 2.0 account linking</strong>.
    When you enable the Alexa skill, you will be prompted to link your Prep &amp; Provide account.
    Upon linking, Alexa receives a secure access token that allows it to read your recipes and grocery
    list on your behalf.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Alexa does not receive your email address or password.</li>
    <li>The access token is used only to fulfill voice requests you initiate (e.g., "Alexa, what's on my grocery list?").</li>
    <li>You can unlink your account at any time through the Alexa app, which immediately revokes access.</li>
    <li>Amazon's handling of your data through Alexa is governed by <a href="https://www.amazon.com/privacy" style="color: var(--heritage-gold);">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Information Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, trade, or share your personal information with third parties for their own purposes. Your data is shared only in the following limited circumstances:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Alexa integration:</strong> As described above, an access token is shared with Amazon when you enable the skill.</li>
    <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law, court order, or to protect the rights and safety of our users or the public.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We retain your account information and app data for as long as your account remains active.
    You can delete your account and all associated data directly within the App at any time.
    Upon deletion, your data will be permanently removed from our systems within 30 days,
    except where retention is required by law.
  </p>

  <h2>6. How to Delete Your Account</h2>
  <p>
    You can delete your Prep &amp; Provide account and all associated data from within the App.
    See our <a href="/legal/delete-account-prep-and-provide" style="color: var(--heritage-gold);">account deletion page</a> for step-by-step instructions.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Prep &amp; Provide is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect
    personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child under 13 has provided us
    with personal information, please contact us and we will promptly delete it.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Security</h2>
  <p>
    We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your information against
    unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no method of transmission over the internet
    or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the
    "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the App after changes
    are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:<br />
    <strong>Legacy Renovations SGF</strong><br />
    Springfield, Missouri<br />
    <a href="mailto:dustin@legacyrenovationssgf.com" style="color: var(--heritage-gold);">dustin@legacyrenovationssgf.com</a>
  </p>

</LegalLayout>
